# Environment variables for AI Newsletter Generator
#
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS:
# 1. Copy this file to .env.local
# 2. Fill in any API keys you want to use as defaults
# 3. Keep .env.local in .gitignore to prevent credential exposure
# 4. Never commit .env.local to version control
#
# NOTE: API keys can also be managed through the app's Settings modal.
# Keys stored via the Settings UI are saved in the local SQLite database.
# Environment variables below serve as fallbacks if not configured in the UI.

# === OPTIONAL API KEYS (can also be set in Settings UI) ===

# Admin email (required for API key lookup from SQLite)
ADMIN_EMAIL=your-email@example.com

# Claude API Key (for newsletter generation)
# Get from: https://console.anthropic.com/
VITE_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# Stability AI API Key (for image generation)
# Get from: https://platform.stability.ai/
VITE_STABILITY_API_KEY=sk-...

# Brave Search API Key (for web search grounding)
# Get from: https://api.search.brave.com/
VITE_BRAVE_SEARCH_API_KEY=BSA...

# === GOOGLE CLOUD CONFIGURATION (Required for Google Workspace) ===
# Configure these in Google Cloud Console for Drive/Sheets/Gmail integration

# Google API Key (for general API access)
GOOGLE_API_KEY=AIza...

# Google OAuth Client ID (for sign-in)
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=123456789-xxx.apps.googleusercontent.com
